OL,3,CKeir Starmer massively shrinks
OL,4,CLabour's green investments
OL,6,FThat #28 billion every year becomes
OL,7,Fjust #23.7 billion over an entire five-
OL,8,Fyear parliament, or an average of
OL,9,F#4.74 billion per annum.
OL,11,FThat said, perhaps the more apt
OL,12,Fcomparison is #18 billion contra the
OL,13,Fnew lower #4.74 billion, because
OL,14,Flatterly Starmer and the shadow
OL,15,Fchancellor Rachel Reeves netted
OL,16,Finvestment being committed now by this
OL,17,Fgovernment off the #28 billion.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/10
