OL,3,CKeir Starmer massively shrinks
OL,4,CLabour's green investments
OL,6,FThis is true, but there are plenty of
OL,7,Feconomists who would argue that the
OL,8,F#28 billion was not only affordable
OL,9,Fbut the minimum necessary to re-start
OL,10,FUK economic growth and improve the
OL,11,FUK's climate-change resilience - the
OL,12,Fmore so since it was anyway
OL,13,Fconditional on a Labour government
OL,14,Fmeeting its fiscal rules or debt
OL,15,Fconstraints.
