OL,3,CKeir Starmer massively shrinks
OL,4,CLabour's green investments
OL,6,FThis is not the only big fiscal change
OL,7,Fannounced by Starmer and Reeves today.
OL,8,FThey are also allocating the proceeds
OL,9,Fof a higher-rate and elongated oil-and-
OL,10,Fgas windfall tax to financing part of
OL,11,Fit what it styles as its Green
OL,12,FProsperity Plan.
OL,14,FAs a result, the #4.74 billion a year
OL,15,Fgreen investment would be funded to
OL,16,Fthe tune of #2.2 billion by the
OL,17,Fwindfall tax and just #2.6 billion
OL,18,Ffrom new borrowing.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/10
