OL,3,CKeir Starmer massively shrinks
OL,4,CLabour's green investments
OL,6,FStarmer and Reeves insist they remain
OL,7,Fcommitted to their pledge to ensure
OL,8,Fall power generated in the UK will
OL,9,Femit net zero carbon dioxide by 2030,
OL,10,Fvia burying CO2 from gas power
OL,11,Fstations (carbon capture and storage),
OL,12,Fbuilding much more renewable
OL,13,Fgeneration (onshore and offshore wind,
OL,14,Fnuclear and so on) and accelerating
OL,15,Fgrid connections.
