OL,3,CKeir Starmer massively shrinks
OL,4,CLabour's green investments
OL,6,FThe cost of the number of homes Labour
OL,7,Fis now promising to insulate and make
OL,8,Fmore energy efficient in the course of
OL,9,Fa parliament is being slashed from #6
OL,10,Fbillion every year to #6.6 billion
OL,11,Fover the course of an entire
OL,12,Fparliament. It means just 5 million
OL,13,Fhomes that are cold and drafty will be
OL,14,Fbrought up to basic standard in five
OL,15,Fyears out of 16 million that require
OL,16,Fthe upgrade.
